Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:51.70,Voice Haruka,,0,0,0,,À...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:57.58,Voice Haruka,,0,0,0,,Chào buổi sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:07.17,Voice Haruka,,0,0,0,,Không có gì.
